nodes.text: Work Horse Co., Ltd. is credited for the strategic layout of Star Wars: Rogue Squadron: The Official Nintendo Player's Guide, the strategy guide for the 1998 Nintendo 64 video game Star Wars: Rogue Squadron. Its contributing members on the project included "Jumpin'" Jack Yushi, Naoyuki Kayama, Toshinori Sato, and Yoshiyuki Oshino.
